     "# Knowledge Graph RAG Implementation\n",
     "\n",
     "This notebook demonstrates building a Knowledge Graph RAG system.\n",
     "\n",
     "## What You'll Learn\n",
     "\n",
     "1. **Knowledge Graphs** - What they are and why they matter\n",
     "2. **Graph Extraction** - Using LLMs to extract entities and relationships\n",
     "3. **Hybrid Retrieval** - Combining vector search with graph traversal\n",
     "4. **Entity-Based Queries** - Answering complex relational questions\n",
     "\n",
     "## What is Knowledge Graph RAG?\n",
     "\n",
     "Knowledge Graph RAG enhances classic RAG by:\n",
     "\n",
     "- **Structured Understanding** - Understands entities and their relationships\n",
     "- **Multi-hop Reasoning** - Can answer questions requiring multiple steps\n",
     "- **Relationship-Aware** - Knows HOW entities connect, not just WHICH are similar\n",
     "\n",
     "## Classic RAG vs KG-RAG\n",
     "\n",
     "| Aspect | Classic RAG | KG-RAG |\n",
     "|--------|-------------|--------|\n",
     "| **Retrieval** | Semantic similarity | Graph traversal |\n",
     "| **Structure** | Flat documents | Entities + relationships |\n",
     "| **Complex queries** | Limited | Excellent (multi-hop) |\n",
     "| **Setup complexity** | Lower | Higher |\n",
     "\n",
     "## Architecture\n",
     "\n",
     "```\n",
     "┌─────────────┐     ┌─────────────┐     ┌─────────────┐\n",
     "│  Document   │────▶│ LLM Graph   │────▶│   Neo4j     │\n",
     "│   Source    │     │ Transformer │     │  Database   │\n",
     "└─────────────┘     └─────────────┘     └──────┬──────┘\n",
     "                                                │\n",
     "                        ┌───────────────────────┤\n",
     "                        │                       │\n",
     "                        ▼                       ▼\n",
     "                 ┌─────────────┐         ┌─────────────┐\n",
     "                 │   Vector    │         │   Graph    │\n",
     "                 │   Search    │         │  Traversal │\n",
     "                 └──────┬──────┘         └──────┬──────┘\n",
     "                        │                       │\n",
     "                        └───────────┬───────────┘\n",
     "                                    ▼\n",
     "                          ┌─────────────────┐\n",
     "                          │   Hybrid        │\n",
     "                          │   Retrieval     │\n",
     "                          └────────┬────────┘\n",
     "                                   │\n",
     "                                   ▼\n",
    ─────────────────┐\ "                          ┌n",
     "                          │   LLM Answer    │\n",
     "                          │   Generation    │\n",
     "                          └─────────────────┘\n",
     "```"
    ]
   },
