     "## Create Sample Data with Relationships\n",
     "\n",
     "**What:** Creating sample documents about entities and their relationships.\n",
     "\n",
     "**Why:** Knowledge Graphs work with structured data - entities (nodes) and their relationships (edges). We'll extract these from text documents.\n",
     "\n",
     "## Understanding the Data Structure\n",
     "\n",
     "Our sample data describes Apple Inc with multiple entity types:\n",
     "\n",
     "| Entity | Type | Relationships |\n",
     "|--------|------|--------------|\n",
     "| Apple | Company | Founded by, Located in, Produces |\n",
     "| Steve Jobs | Person | Co-founded, Founded NeXT, Founded Pixar |\n",
     "| Tim Cook | Person | CEO of (succeeded Jobs) |\n",
     "| Cupertino | Location | Headquarters of |\n     "\n",
     "> This structured information enables complex queries like \"Who succeeded Steve Jobs as CEO?\" which requires understanding the PREDECESSOR relationship."
    ]
   },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "Created 5 sample documents\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "from langchain_core.documents import Document\n",
    "\n",
    "sample_docs = [\n",
    "    Document(\n",
    "        page_content=\"Apple was founded in 1976 by Steve Jobs, Steve Wozniak, and Ronald Wayne.\",\n",
    "        metadata={\"source\": \"doc1\", \"type\": \"company\"}\n",
    "    ),\n",
    "    Document(\n",
    "        page_content=\"Apple's headquarters is located in Cupertino, California.\",\n",
    "        metadata={\"source\": \"doc2\", \"type\": \"location\"}\n",
    "    ),\n",
    "    Document(\n",
    "        page_content=\"Steve Jobs co-founded Apple and later founded NeXT and Pixar.\",\n",
    "        metadata={\"source\": \"doc3\", \"type\": \"person\"}\n",
    "    ),\n",
    "    Document(\n",
    "        page_content=\"Tim Cook became CEO of Apple in 2011, succeeding Steve Jobs.\",\n",
    "        metadata={\"source\": \"doc4\", \"type\": \"person\"}\n",
    "    ),\n",
    "    Document(\n",
    "        page_content=\"Apple produces iPhone, Mac, iPad, and Apple Watch.\",\n",
    "        metadata={\"source\": \"doc5\", \"type\": \"product\"}\n",
    "    ),\n",
    "]\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"Created {len(sample_docs)} sample documents\")"
   ]
  },
