     "## Query the KG-RAG System\n",
     "\n",
     "**What:** Running queries through the hybrid retrieval pipeline.\n",
     "\n",
     "## Why KG-RAG Shines\n",
     "\n",
     "The query \"Who founded Apple and what products do they make?\" requires:\n",
     "\n",
     "1. **Entity: Apple** - Identify the company\n",
     "2. **Relationship: FOUNDED_BY** - Get founders from graph\n",
     "3. **Relationship: PRODUCES** - Get products from graph\n",
     "4. **Combine** - Merge both relationship results\n",
     "\n",
     "## Interpreting Results\n",
     "The answer combines:\n",
     "- **Vector context**: \"Apple was founded in 1976...\"\n",
     "- **Graph relationships**: \"Apple --FOUNDED_BY--> Steve Jobs\"\n",
     "- **Graph relationships**: \"Apple --PRODUCES--> iPhone\"\n",
     "\n",
     "> This multi-source context gives richer answers than classic RAG alone!"
    ]
   },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "Question: Who founded Apple and what products do they make?\n",
      "\n",
      "Answer: Apple was founded by Steve Jobs, Steve Wozniak, and Ronald Wayne, but later primarily by Steve Jobs. Apple makes iPhone, Mac, iPad, and Apple Watch.\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "from langchain_core.runnables import RunnableLambda, RunnablePassthrough\n",
    "from langchain_core.output_parsers import StrOutputParser\n",
    "from langchain_core.prompts import PromptTemplate\n",
    "\n",
    "# Helper function to format documents\n",
    "def format_docs(docs):\n",
    "    return \"\\n\\n\".join(doc.page_content for doc in docs)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Create QA chain using LCEL\n",
    "prompt = PromptTemplate.from_template(\"Use the following context to answer the question. If you cannot find the answer in the context, say you don't know.\\n\\nContext: {context}\\nQuestion: {question}\\nAnswer:\")\n",
    "\n",
    "qa_chain = (\n",
    "    {\"context\": RunnableLambda(lambda x: format_docs(retriever.retrieve(x))), \"question\": RunnablePassthrough()}\n",
    "    | prompt\n",
    "    | llm\n",
    "    | StrOutputParser()\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Query\n",
    "query = \"Who founded Apple and what products do they make?\"\n",
    "result = qa_chain.invoke(query)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"Question: {query}\")\n",
    "print(f\"\\nAnswer: {result}\")\n"
   ]
  },
