     "## Next Steps\n",
     "\n",
     "### Production Improvements\n",
     "\n",
     "| Improvement | Description |\n",
     "|-------------|-------------|\n",
     "| **Neo4j Setup** | Set up persistent Neo4j database |\n",
     "| **Cypher Queries** | Use Cypher for complex graph traversals |\n",
     "| **Entity Resolution** | Handle duplicate entities (e.g., \"Apple\" vs \"Apple Inc.\") |\n",
     "| **Relationship Types** | Add more relationship types (WORKS_AT, LOCATED_IN, etc.) |\n",
     "| **Graph Embeddings** | Use graph neural networks for embedding |\n",
     "\n",
     "### When to Use KG-RAG\n",
     "✅ **Great for:**\n",
     "- Complex, multi-hop questions\n",
     "- Relationship-heavy domains (org charts, supply chains)\n",
     "- When you need to understand HOW things connect\n",
     "\n",
     "❌ **Classic RAG may be better:**\n",
     "- Simple Q&A with direct answers\n",
     "- Large unstructured document collections\n",
     "- When setup complexity is a concern\n",
     "\n",
     "### Learning Path\n",
     "1. **Notebook 1**: Classic RAG (foundations)\n",
     "2. **Notebook 3**: Agentic RAG (autonomous agents)\n",
     "3. **Notebook 6**: Advanced retrieval techniques"
    ]
   }
